&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a hands-on role. You will architect, deploy, and maintain multi-carrier bonded connectivity solutions end to end, and act as the technical bridge between our field operations and our carrier partners.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
